doctype
html.ng-app(lang="en")
  head
    title #{title} - My Site
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='/stylesheets/bootstrap.css')
    script(src='/scripts/bootstrap.js')
    script(src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.3.14/angular.min.js")
    meta(name="viewport" content="")

  nav.navbar.navbar-default
    div.container-fluid
      div.navbar-header




  body.container(ng-controller="macroController")
    div.col-sm-10.col-sm-offset-1
      div.panel.panel-default
        div.panel-heading
          h4 Purpose
        div.panel-body
          p.col-sm-10.col-sm-offset-1.
            In the day and age of highly processed foods and copius amounts of temptation, we're kept in the dark about not only 
            what's in the food we're consuming but also how much of it we're supposed to have in order to maintain a weight that 
            we would desire. This is where this calculator comes in. By using some personal information you'll be able to get a 
            better idea of how many calories you'll need every day to accomplish the fitness goals that you most desire, whatever 
            they may be.
    div.col-sm-10.col-sm-offset-1
      div.panel.panel-default
        div.panel-heading
          h4 Personal Info
        div.panel-body
          div.col-sm-12
          form.form-horizontal
            div.form-group
              label.col-sm-2.control-label Age
              div.col-sm-8
                input.form-control(type="number" placeholder="27" id="age")
            div.form-group
              label.col-sm-2.control-label Height
              div.col-sm-4
                input.form-control(type="number" placeholder="feet" id="feet")
              div.col-sm-4
                input.form-control(type="number" placeholder="inches" id="inches")
            div.form-group
              label.col-sm-2.control-label Weight
              div.col-sm-8
                input.form-control(type="number" placeholder="in lbs" id="weight")
            div.form-group
              label.col-sm-2.control-label Gender
              div.col-sm-4
                button.btn.btn-block Male
              div.col-sm-4
                button.btn.btn-block Female

    footer